    "level_2_statistical": "One loop of length 3, with one delay edge (T→F). Monitoring coverage is an exogenous moderator with one negative link into Fires.",
    "level_3_perceptual": "The dominant loop is balancing: velocity is self-limiting through debt accumulation and delayed fire-fighting, not through external constraint.",
